{"tid":2426224,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"林書豪稱被叫新冠病毒 聯盟允諾進行介入調查","createTime":"2021-02-28T02:39:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-28T08:13:54.000Z","uid":212249,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"2c58de98df970741dad64072e28dbb4d02865762","tid":2426224,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T02:39:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pgw-udn-com-tw.cdn.ampproject.org/i/s/pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2021/02/27/1/11792161.jpeg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=1050\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw-udn-com-tw.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fi%2Fs%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2021%2F02%2F27%2F1%2F11792161.jpeg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D1050&h=485e6300&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n林書豪日前透過Facebook發聲，盼外界別再歧視亞裔美國人，甚至自曝曾在場上被對手以「新冠病毒」稱呼，此事經他本人揭露後，聯盟也表示將介入調查。<br />\n<br />\n《ESPN》記者史比爾斯（Marc J. Spears）表示，G聯盟官方稱會對林書豪說法進行查證，儘管他並未指出事發時間點，勇士主帥柯爾（Steve Kerr）也表達支持。<br />\n<br />\n「我才看到他的發文而已，內容很有力，當然提到這點時有些模糊，所以希望官方能釐清。而我非常支持林書豪願替亞裔美國人受種族歧視歧視說話」，柯爾說。"},{"pid":"e3897c1b610f6a07402d621c13cfea20bac604bd","tid":2426224,"uid":5178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T02:42:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fb92dd2786fa441ebf1e6d4e0e436619158dfbe","tid":2426224,"uid":40272,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T02:52:06.000Z","msg":"係支那累你"},{"pid":"29f845a0a2eda2061a67409da5dd4233c2f73469","tid":2426224,"uid":4574,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T02:59:19.000Z","msg":"你首先是中國人"},{"pid":"55358ce018c48e40ec6c2c57ac01527dd3d28833","tid":2426224,"uid":71133,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T03:03:28.000Z","msg":"開始明點解呢條友去到邊都唔受歡迎，有親咩事都係玩篤灰扮慘十足十讀書個種冇朋友既濕鳩同學<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pi